{"tid":621421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳金正恩願放棄核武  前提是美國確保政權穩固 兩國正進行秘密對話 準備領袖會面","createTime":"2018-04-08T09:56:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T15:00:12.000Z","uid":48083,"like":10,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"b72a49ad37576bba8a8d74acfcc3918f0afb0a0d","tid":621421,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T09:56:09.000Z","msg":"寰宇新聞網／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n根據日本媒體報導，北韓領導人金正恩日前密訪中國，請習近平協助提出的交換條件，是要美國「堅定保證」北韓政權安全，而北韓則可以「完全放棄」核武。據傳金正恩說，北韓願意邀請外界檢視核子場地，並縮短非核化進程，並計畫在川金會時，提出兩國建交的提案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://globalnewstv.com.tw/傳金正恩願放棄核武-前提是美國確保政權穩固/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fglobalnewstv.com.tw%2F%E5%82%B3%E9%87%91%E6%AD%A3%E6%81%A9%E9%A1%98%E6%94%BE%E6%A3%84%E6%A0%B8%E6%AD%A6-%E5%89%8D%E6%8F%90%E6%98%AF%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%A2%BA%E4%BF%9D%E6%94%BF%E6%AC%8A%E7%A9%A9%E5%9B%BA%2F&d=Xtjo5GBSm4Pu%2BzG1FjlExMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=16f3dd87\" target=\"_blank\">http://globalnewstv.com.tw/傳金正恩願放棄核武-前提是美國確保政權穩固/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【為兩國領袖會面做準備】 <br />\n【CNN:美朝進行秘密直接對話】<br />\n<br />\n美國(CNN)報道，美國和北韓正秘密進行直接對話，為美朝領袖會面做準備。<br />\n<br />\n統籌工作由兩國情報部門主導，報道指北韓首都平壤及蒙古首都烏蘭巴托，都有可能是會談地點。<br />\n<br />\n會面日期最快是五月底，甚至六月。<br />\n<br />\n#有線新聞　#美國　#北韓　#秘密對話　#美朝領袖　#情報部門<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/829555390569864/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F829555390569864%2F&d=Xtjo5GBSm4Pu%2BzG1FjlExMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=82827008\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/829555390569864/</a>"},{"pid":"681eca2f8876c8b5439aa8746a027252f2979f7f","tid":621421,"uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T09:57:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真唔真"},{"pid":"124eeb294132f577b4e576d8c2c87084282ad1b8","tid":621421,"uid":50663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T09:58:48.000Z","msg":"竟然金仔要跪低？"},{"pid":"d6f5d1425efda40652908c2d26bceedfe37128c2","tid":621421,"uid":75072,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T09:59:19.000Z","msg":"On9先信"},{"pid":"fd19d064e3bd0c7eafacb0ef7bba4b4c8c065df8","tid":621421,"uid":50457,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T09:59:46.000Z","msg":"Trump: 前提要同支那脫交，同台灣結交<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba6aa26851e5d04e157d9f9a68bdc042cb631335","tid":621421,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:00:20.000Z","msg":"點保證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28793985f409e04e3a3647a9b9aee16f17feae1d","tid":621421,"uid":29093,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:00:42.000Z","msg":"即係 北韓想做美國佬隻狗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<br />\n唔怪得 雜種咁急召見 小金啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f64b19ac9d1f865582dc4c97f13bcbdff24536af","tid":621421,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:01:26.000Z","msg":"有無咁天真？最多走中國回頭路 搵個地方行資本主義"},{"pid":"8f90a0279c140c44bb876538c4fe902ebbcc1115","tid":621421,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:01:34.000Z","msg":"日媒：金正恩向習近平表示願意重啟六方會談　<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2018-04-05 23:07<br />\n最後更新日期：2018-04-05 23:07<br />\n日本傳媒周四（5日）報道，朝鮮最高領導人金正恩向中國與國家主席習近平表示，同意重啟六方會談。<br />\n<br />\n《日經新聞》引述消息報道，金正恩與習近平上星期舉行會談期間，表達有關意願。消息又指金正恩不排除會在5月與美國總統特朗普會面時表達同樣意願，但目前仍未確定美朝會談能否順利召開。<br />\n<br />\n中國官員暫未有就事件回應。<br />\n<br />\n六方會談2003年起啟動，談判由朝鮮、南韓、中國、美國、日本及俄羅斯六國共同參與，旨在解決朝鮮核問題，會議自2008年起暫停至今。"},{"pid":"59712018ab2265f0294f63019a892c5a09e158ca","tid":621421,"uid":90601,"like